OL,3,CKing's state visit shows need for
OL,4,CWhite House ballroom, says Donald Trump
OL,6,FDonald Trump has pointed to the
OL,7,Fupcoming state visit of the King to
OL,8,Fhighlight the need for a controversial
OL,9,F400 million dollar (#301 million)
OL,10,Fballroom at the White House.
OL,12,FThe US president argued the
OL,13,Fdevelopment was necessary to entertain
OL,14,Fa large number of people when hosting
OL,15,Fforeign dignitaries and world leaders.
OL,17,FThe 90,000-square foot project, which
OL,18,Fsaw the East Wing torn down last
OL,19,FOctober, has been the subject of a
OL,20,Flegal challenge in a bid to halt
OL,21,Fconstruction.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
