OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774696008
OL,3,CKing's state visit shows need for
OL,4,CWhite House ballroom, says Donald Trump
OL,6,FThe White House is sited on federal
OL,7,Fparkland. A panel reviewing the plans,
OL,8,Fwhich is headed by a top aide to the
OL,9,Fpresident, is due to hold a final vote
OL,10,Fon the scheme on April 2.
OL,12,FEarlier this year, the US Commission
OL,13,Fof Fine Arts, whose members were
OL,14,Fappointed by Trump, gave unanimous
OL,15,Fbacking to the proposal.
OL,17,FSpeaking to a group of farmers as he
OL,18,Foverlooked the building site, the
OL,19,Fpresident and billionaire developer
OL,20,Fdeclared: "I love construction."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
