OL,3,CKing's state visit shows need for
OL,4,CWhite House ballroom, says Donald Trump
OL,6,FThe privately funded ballroom
OL,7,Fdevelopment, which is designed to hold
OL,8,F1,000 guests, is due to be completed
OL,9,Fbefore the end of Trump's presidency
OL,10,Fin 2029.
OL,12,FEarlier this week, the president
OL,13,Fdenied transatlantic tensions over the
OL,14,FIran war would affect the King's
OL,15,Fplanned trip to the US.
OL,17,FThere have been calls for the historic
OL,18,Froyal trip to be scrapped or delayed
OL,19,Fbecause of the ongoing Middle East
OL,20,Fcrisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
