OL,3,CKing's state visit shows need for
OL,4,CWhite House ballroom, says Donald Trump
OL,6,FThe tour has yet to be officially
OL,7,Fannounced, but the King and Queen are
OL,8,Fexpected to visit Washington and New
OL,9,FYork in April to mark the 250th
OL,10,Fanniversary of American independence.
OL,12,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,13,Fweekly podcast about the royal family,
OL,14,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,15,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
